messages.message: what’s the rule around pip-installable packages and UDFs? Like, if we wanted to use `dateutil` in a UDF, is there any support? Or is it only out of a list of pre-selected packages like `requests`?
(I presume if it is supported there’s some process for getting the lib installed or uploading an .egg or something)
The docs at https://www.instabase.com/docs/content/apps/refiner/extending-refiner.html aren’t clear about what’s supported
